description: it was a perfectly sunny beautiful day and I knew it was, appreciate it was.  had this yearning to go take a walk outside today but I duno wtf is the matter  I just chose to stay in bed and cried half the day while looking at the window,  knowing it was a beautiful sunny day and I'm beating myself up for feeling shitty  for some assholes that did shitty thing that I should have moved on from since .  but I would pick this kind of day in a heartbeat than those old days  that lasted a few years when I couldn't afford for food for my family or my kids.  did I waste this day by diving into the darkness of my own mind's cave ? it was a perfectly beautiful sunny day . ooakosimo
